classDiagram
    class DashboardConfigPrototype {
        -Dict~str, Any~ _config
        +__init__()
        +clone() Dict~str, Any~
        +clone_for_user(user_id: int, default_location: str, theme: str) Dict~str, Any~
        +get_minimal_config() Dict~str, Any~
    }

    class DashboardConfig {
        +str layout
        +int refresh_interval
        +List~Widget~ widgets
        +Dict preferences
        +int user_id
    }

    class Widget {
        +str id
        +str type
        +Dict position
        +Dict settings
    }

    class Preferences {
        +str default_location
        +List~str~ favorite_stations
        +str theme
    }

    DashboardConfigPrototype ..> DashboardConfig : creates clone
    DashboardConfig o-- Widget : contains
    DashboardConfig o-- Preferences : contains

    note for DashboardConfigPrototype "Prototype Pattern:\nProvee configuracion base\nque puede ser clonada y\npersonalizada para cada usuario"
